## API Endpoints

```
# Analytics Dashboard
GET   /api/v1/analytics/dashboard                   (role-based widgets)
GET   /api/v1/analytics/dashboard/fee-collection-today
GET   /api/v1/analytics/dashboard/outstanding-dues
GET   /api/v1/analytics/dashboard/attendance-snapshot
GET   /api/v1/analytics/dashboard/admission-funnel

# Student Performance Reports
GET   /api/v1/reports/student-performance?exam_id=&stream_id=
GET   /api/v1/reports/student-performance/{studentId}/trend
GET   /api/v1/reports/at-risk-students?threshold=

# Financial Reports
GET   /api/v1/reports/fee-collection?from=&to=&class_id=&fee_type_id=
GET   /api/v1/reports/outstanding-dues?stream_id=&aging=
GET   /api/v1/reports/revenue-trend?period=monthly
GET   /api/v1/reports/receipt-register?from=&to=

# Attendance Reports
GET   /api/v1/reports/attendance-summary?date=&stream_id=
GET   /api/v1/reports/attendance-monthly?month=&stream_id=
GET   /api/v1/reports/chronic-absentees?threshold=75

# Exports
GET   /api/v1/reports/{reportType}/export?format=pdf|excel&...filters
```

