| Student Performance | `/analytics/performance` | Class/exam performance analysis |
| Fee Collection Report | `/analytics/fee-collection` | Filterable fee collection view |
| Outstanding Dues | `/analytics/outstanding-dues` | Aging analysis with student list |
| Attendance Report | `/analytics/attendance` | Daily/monthly attendance reports |
| Admission Analytics | `/analytics/admissions` | Pipeline funnel and trends |

